text: RT @kaisisokay: A blockchain attempting to become a brand challenges the foundations of the brands built on top if it.  Solana gets so muchâ€¦

A blockchain attempting to become a brand challenges the foundations of the brands built on top if it.  Solana gets so much right when it comes to tech, events and community building.

I'm less concerned about the actual content of the Accelerate ad, and more about Solana's decision to find a brand voice.  It's partially why building multi chain was important for Okay even though our numbers clearly don't support my claim at this moment... But if we're looking at long term, blockchains are as young as the brands built on them, and our products being tethered to their financial intrinsic value is already a huge commitment for brands building on top.

To have to deal with brand voice experiments on top of that just makes things more complicated.

Tech should be neutral. Brands aren't.
